{title: Textblock Section}

{start_of_verse}
[G]Some songs need a [C]block of text
[D]That is not lyrics [G]or chords
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_textblock}
This is a textblock section. It contains free-form text
that is not treated as lyrics. No chord parsing happens
inside a textblock.

It might contain stage directions, performance notes,
or other supplementary information that should be
rendered verbatim without chord processing.

    Indentation is preserved as-is.
    Multiple lines with consistent indentation.
        Even deeper indentation works.
{end_of_textblock}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]After the text [G]block
[D]The song continues [G]on
{end_of_chorus}

{start_of_textblock}
Performance Notes:
- Start with soft picking on verse 1
- Build intensity through the chorus
- Full strumming on verse 2
- Gentle ending with arpeggiated chords
{end_of_textblock}
